<p><span style="font-size:125%;"><strong><a href="/you-can-t-win-them-all">第4章</a> - <span style="font-family: 'Berkshire Swash', cursive;">You Can't Win Them All</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:125%;"><strong><a href="/be-strange-or-be-forgotten">第5章</a> - <span style="font-family: 'Berkshire Swash', cursive;">Be Strange or Be Forgotten</span></strong></span></p>
